                  <p style="padding-top: 0px; " class="paragraph_style_14">Therefore, [my friends], so that you may not be in the same state as most people and ... <br /></p>
                  <p style="padding-top: 0px; " class="paragraph_style_19"><br /></p>
                  <p style="padding-top: 0px; " class="paragraph_style_19">Fr. 140<br /></p>
