                  <p style="padding-top: 0px; " class="paragraph_style_19"><br /></p>
                  <p style="padding-top: 0px; " class="paragraph_style_19">Fr. 144<br /></p>
                  <p style="padding-top: 0px; " class="paragraph_style_14">...... worse.<br /></p>
                  <p style="padding-top: 0px; " class="paragraph_style_14">Coughing complains [scarcely cause] any [trouble to the chronic sufferer] ...<br /></p>
