                  <p style="padding-top: 0px; " class="paragraph_style_14">As for the [argument] concerning [madness] (since some [suffer from this also), it is to be put] like this. In the first place ............................................................................................................. [Secondly], let us not be unaware [that] madness [not] by old age, but [by] some other [cause of] natural [origin]. <br /></p>
